{
  "stem": "6257.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And suddenly after a kind of lull, when no one was speaking, the Germans weren't coming into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Suddenly, they were there finding people again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this man friend of my mother's was from the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came and had a gun and led us to some hiding place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I think that-- then somehow when things quiet and he led us through the-- the [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Tebbens ?] place.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and it was-- that was really terrible, that sort of-- that particular memory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That older people who worked in the factory were told to go to some-- probably Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm not sure where they were told to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were supposed to be reselected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they were told that they could come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they sort of-- my uncle and the aunts, and so on, who were working in the factory all went.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we and my grandparents hid again in some big bunker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know who again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were lots-- there wasn't just our family, there were lots of families there and some babies crying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was a little bit terrified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that seemed the sort of end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But then they came back, half my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were allowed to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But there were these terrible stories of people poisoning themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They told us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And some-- some families took their children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because the children, none of which were supposed to be allowed back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Also I remember some were brought in coffins, they'd been given injections-- not-- not killed-- smuggled back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And people brought some sort of small children back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that sort of-- [INAUDIBLE] that was--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To pretend that they were dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somehow smuggling them back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
